the 'if' Function/Script and the 'switch' Function/Script are exactly the same thing, just different looks/styles/patterns to them:

```
get input {
  if (result = 0) {
    // blah
  } else if (result = 1) {
    // blah
  } else {
    // blah
  }
}

get input {
  switch (result) {
    case (0) {
      // blah
    }
    case (1) {
      // blah
    }
    default {
      // blah
    }
  }
}
```

